name: Melody McCloskey
bio: Founder of @styleseat the premiere destination to book beauty and barber appointments, angel investor for @cleocapital

social_posts.post_text: The energy of being in a stadium with tens of thousand of people screaming, all watching the same experience is one of the best things on the planet. So fun to see how things work behind the scenes with one of the greatest to ever do it Dick Ebersol, HBIC @susie1q and my love @charlieebersol

Ok natural hair was fine but happy have extensions again, especially since I’m still trying to crawl my way back from 4th trimester hair loss. I have baby hairs popping out all over and we’re welcoming every single one. Life is moving quickly, good things are happening with the business, family is good and those moments always make me nervous.  But why? I’m so used to fighting fires that when there’s a brief pause I’m not sure what to do. Good thing to reflect on, but mostly this is a post about new hair lol.

Proud wife shoutout to @charlieebersol, EP of @therecruitseries_netflix , Adam Ciralsky who‘s life the show is based off of and @alexihawley who wrote the show. Exited to celebrate you! LOVED the first episode and can’t wait to watch more. Also Roger Carstens, the guy in the third photo led the team that brough Brittney Griner home, but also watches tv so he was there too 😂 @styleseat @colbymakeup

This is Eric, who joined @styleseat a year ago. He’d been using another service but didn’t get many new clients. StyleSeat brought him more than $50k in revenue in the past year. He is also brilliant in terms of how he runs his business. I met him because I randomly asked @charlieebersol who his barber was because I love meeting community members. I teared up hearing his story. Honestly it’s moments like this that make my work feel worthwhile.
Christmas morning. Everyone was thrilled I picked the hottest pajamas on the planet while on a desert vacation. We’re all sweating profusely and removed these minutes after the photo.

Happy late 40th birthday to the love of my life @charlieebersol. It’s been a journey! I admire how hard you work and how much you love your family, friends and dogs kids. Thank you for being an incredible partner and dad. I love you to the 🌙
@StyleSeat / @loveseen photo shoot with @jennalyonsnyc was 🔥🔥 more shots coming soon
Rihanna’s concert was 🔥
First day of school and last day of school. Stop growing up! Congrats on the milestone baby girl I love being your mama.
Congratulations to @anniegerhart and @ramsayphilips7 we loved celebrating you! ❤️
For a one year old little mama gets it

Got to visit the set of @nbaontnt !!! So much funnn. I fell in love with this show after watching the documentary about it (even if you don’t love sports it’s an amazing watch). They are the best sports show on tv. Also I can’t believe the crew stays until 1-2am to film i had to get home and go to sleep half way through I could not hang 👵🏻😂 #atlanta

I had the pleasure of meeting @iambrandiharvey for her @vaultempowers series. She took the conversation to a much deeper level than I expected! We got into the big topics and had so much fun I laughed my big hyena laugh that I’ve spent years hiding 😂

What a joy to celebrate @alicemariefree ‘s 5th anniversary of freedom. I’ve had the pleasure of getting to know her this year. We’ve had a lot of fun and I’ve learned a lot from her. She has a gift of seeing beauty in everyone and everything, and making everyone around her glow. There were tears but mostly a lot of laughter tonight.

This is the first photo Amara has taken of me. I’m starting to really pay attention to how she sees me and how I want her to see me. I believe my girls appeared in this world as whole people and my job is to give them as much confidence and support as I can. I try my hardest to never be preoccupied, busy on my phone or stressed no matter what crisis is going on. I want her to know I feel lucky to be her mama. It is hard. And there are so many times that she says mom! And I want to say hold on I’m doing something, because there’s an urgent issue or I’m on a call or finishing an email that needs to get out before whatever whatever. But no matter how important it is, and there is always something important to be preoccupied with, she will only be 4 for a little while longer.

If you need any more proof that makeup artists are magicians!! Thank you @88manuel88 for your amazing artistry, and your gift for making people feel wonderful in your chair. You also somehow got this elder millennial to make a TikTok so you can do anything you put your mind to 😂

I just found these on my phone, from Charlie’s 40th this year! He partnered with the Imagineers to create a theme park to raise money for @blackbanksmatter . I got a bunch of texts the next day saying we should do it every year 😂 happy birthday baby. Even if I’m late 💋
Happy Father’s Day to the best dad in the world. Thank you for being a loving, patient figure in their lives. They loved you to pieces and so do I.

I am overjoyed to welcome @jkhaliph to the family. Congratulations @summermcc for picking a good one. He is generous in loving my sister, funny, joyful and such a gift to us as well. Excited to have more love in all our lives ❤️❤️❤️

I’ve always been ambitious, but have wrestled with the space between what I want to do and what I thought i was capable of doing. Before creating @styleseat I would think about it often, and every moment of excitement would come with thoughts about how I could never start it, or hire people or fundraise. Here’s the thing. I’m a non-technical founder from a regular school who bootstrapped for a long time before being able to fundraise. But I can do hard things, and I have GRIT. Starting and running a company has taught me what I’m capable of, and those lessons are my proudest moments. Now that I’ve done it I am not scared of what comes next because I can do it again. And if I can do it anyone can, no matter their size experience or background.

Happy birthday Kaia! You’ve brought more joy to me than I could have ever imagined. You made it clear from day one you were very different from your sister and we love you so much for it. You are tricky, have a lot of ideas on how the world should work, and you love a good pair of sunglasses. I’m so thankful for my baby bear 🧸🐻
